quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  59,17,to dono ka injaam yeh howa ke dono dozakh mein ( daakhil hue ) hamesha is mein rahen ge. aur be insafon ki yahi saza hai
  59,18,ae imaan walon! khuda se drtay raho aur har shakhs ko dekhna chahiye ke is ne kal ( yani فردائے qayamat ) ke liyekiya ( samaan ) bheja hai aur ( hum phir kehte hain ke ) khuda se drtay raho be shak khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai
  59,19,aur un logon jaisay nah hona jinhon ne khuda ko bhala diya to khuda ne inhen aisa kardiya ke khud apne tain bhool gay. yeh badkirdar log hain
  59,20,ahal dozakh aur ahal bahisht barabar nahi. ahal bahisht to kamyabi haasil karne walay hain
  59,21,agar hum yeh quran kisi pahar par nazil karte to tum is ko dekhte ke khuda ke khauf se daba aur phataa jata hai. aur yeh baatein hum logon ke liye bayan karte hain taakay woh fikar karen
  59,22,wohi khuda hai jis ke siwa koi mabood nahi. posheeda aur zahir ka jan-nay wala hai woh bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  59,23,wohi khuda hai jis ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi. badshah ( haqeeqi ) pak zaat ( har aib se ) salamti aman dainay wala nigehbaan ghalib zabardast barayi wala. khuda un logon ke shareek muqarrar karne se pak hai
  59,24,wohi khuda ( tamam makhloqaat ka ) khaaliq. ijaad o ikhtraa karne wala soorten bananay wala is ke sab achay se achay naam hain. jitni cheeze asmano aur zameen mein hain sab is ki tasbeeh karti hain aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
